---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Kitchen & Bathroom Remodels"
  description={`Kitchen and bathroom remodeling in Asheville & Hendersonville, NC by licensed plumbers and contractors. Free estimates: call ${site.phone}.`}
  heroTitle="Need Plumbing For Your Kitchen or Bathroom Remodel?"
  heroSubtitle="Start with a free estimate in Asheville or Hendersonville, NC, and let our licensed plumbers and contractors handle the kitchen or bathroom remodel you've been planning."
  heroImage="/images/gallery/gallery-06.jpg"
  listHeading="What We Remodel"
  listItems={[
    'Kitchen remodels: sinks, cabinetry, dishwashers, garbage disposals, counter tops, tile work',
    'Bathroom remodels: showers, sinks, bathtubs, toilets, cabinetry, tile work',
  ]}
  listNote="Still not convinced? Take a look at our testimonials page and give us a call!"
  ctaHeading="Ready to Start Your Remodel?"
>
  <p>
    That garden tub or walk-in shower you've been wanting is closer than you think. Our kitchen
    and bathroom plumbing contractors pull out the dated fixtures and give the room a clean, modern
    look in Asheville or Hendersonville, NC. Call now to talk through what you have in mind.
  </p>

  <h2 class="pt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900">
    Asheville, NC Kitchen and Bathroom Plumbing
  </h2>
  <p>
    We're licensed plumbers and contractors, and we do the work like it's our own home, start to
    finish. We build for every budget and keep the pricing straight: competitive rates, up-front
    numbers, and no hidden fees across the Asheville &amp; Hendersonville, NC areas.
  </p>
  <p>
    Bring us the ideas you've been collecting and we'll help you make them real. Call today to talk
    with one of our contractors:
    <a href={site.phoneHref} class="font-semibold text-drop-600 hover:underline">{site.phone}</a>.
  </p>
  <p>
    <a href="/testimonials" class="font-semibold text-drop-600 hover:underline">Read our reviews &rarr;</a>
  </p>
</ServiceLayout>
